/InitTextBox { userdict /TBy2 3 -1 roll put userdict /TBx2 3 -1 roll put
           userdict /TBy1 3 -1 roll put userdict /TBx1 3 -1 roll put
	   /Boxing true def } def
/ExtendTextBox { Boxing
